summary: An Ordinance confirming, approving and establishing the "Replat of John J. McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle, and Blocks 13, 14, 18, 20 to 29, inclusive and south half of 19 of John J. McGilvra's Second Addition to the City of Seattle," vacating certain original streets and alleys, establishing certain new streets and other public places, adjudicating damages and benefits occasioned thereby, and directing the recording of said replat.
